{"tid":455894,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救連唔到去router","createTime":"2017-11-02T13:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T17:38:04.000Z","uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e12a1ea3b911ee47a4aa30f3c784bcdd883a2a2c","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T13:20:09.000Z","msg":"原本新買番黎個router wifi同電腦都上到網<br />\n但我電腦行到900mbps<br />\n但手機wifi得30mbps<br />\n咁咪係電腦個router firmware到搞下睇下有咩問題<br />\n點知就電腦上唔到網但wifi得<br />\n依加搞咗兩日<br />\n變咗電腦上到網<br />\n但連唔到router 個ip<br />\n手機都連唔到　搞到無wifi用<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/212001_652e01809c8a580973f0f48d06992f7d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F212001_652e01809c8a580973f0f48d06992f7d.png&h=9eb5bff3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"902cf5bd9caf79f1a79babaa205215fb4ba30115","tid":455894,"uid":79546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"你入網路和共用中心<br />\n乙太網路<br />\n內容<br />\n詳細資料"},{"pid":"3eeb86721e1f827878dd4ad5600fa6d593664019","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你入網路和共用中心<br />\n乙太網路<br />\n內容<br />\n詳細資料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/225213_749d5dce34df3ebdb39a0eaa50ae0b79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F225213_749d5dce34df3ebdb39a0eaa50ae0b79.png&h=fd76da10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a57efde07274d5fd2e998a1a5973d4c771fb66","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你入網路和共用中心<br />\n乙太網路<br />\n內容<br />\n詳細資料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依加睇個IPv6 係無網絡存取<br />\n上咗網上行個網開左個IPv6 但都好似唔得"},{"pid":"213e6b93a3e23b1c5256b460166be5a4dd11ebcc","tid":455894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"電腦行緊public IP 係咪錯線 或者行左bridge mode <br />\nReset 過再重新set 過啦"},{"pid":"b2f9458e5022ac051599251529d1652401d040f7","tid":455894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你入網路和共用中心<br />\n乙太網路<br />\n內容<br />\n詳細資料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依加睇個IPv6 係無網絡存取<br />\n上咗網上行個網開左個IPv6 但都好似唔得</blockquote><br />\n唔洗理ipv6"},{"pid":"2f65b7c73b59245123925eed5399f7080d55d3b7","tid":455894,"uid":141062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"reset"},{"pid":"796256046c33f101dcd8a0cb4cb58def046a700f","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你入網路和共用中心<br />\n乙太網路<br />\n內容<br />\n詳細資料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依加睇個IPv6 係無網絡存取<br />\n上咗網上行個網開左個IPv6 但都好似唔得</blockquote><br />\n唔洗理ipv6</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但佢話我依加係無開ipv6 所以連唔到去個router <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af798e3e1f8a5797e2024528a6f7bfcd37fcfa6","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電腦行緊public IP 係咪錯線 或者行左bridge mode <br />\nReset 過再重新set 過啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點reset<br />\n其實我己經成部電腦reset番去幾日前<br />\n依加係上到網但認唔到個router<br />\nset唔到個router"},{"pid":"d1b26a11a69eced6d2eb04b143a7878f82edd4ca","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電腦行緊public IP 係咪錯線 或者行左bridge mode <br />\nReset 過再重新set 過啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琴日就係set router果時有個　模式選擇<br />\n咁我見幅圖係modem<br />\n咁我咪禁落router 果幅圖到(佢話咩AP)<br />\n之後就出哂事<br />\n其實我今日試過係部router 後面個洞到禁過幾次好似有reset過　<br />\n但都係連唔到"},{"pid":"d044a9dae1cb10c44c787904f81bd9a247103a74","tid":455894,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"你reset個router<br />\n用lan線 Router直入電腦<br />\n之後再開翻個詳細資料"},{"pid":"e642321ff802e5b0a78459df783d97928ee2b079","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你reset個router<br />\n用lan線 Router直入電腦<br />\n之後再開翻個詳細資料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依加出去睇番個router <br />\n佢接modem果個燈變左紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/232027_444c545a23cc47dfd6a8b4af16209bb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F232027_444c545a23cc47dfd6a8b4af16209bb4.png&h=bba8877e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"121832f16ad783fb2338ce9943eb29f177298d9a","tid":455894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"Google 下你隻野點reset 啦 <br />\n應該有d recovery tools"},{"pid":"da07dc523e36f0bb7fcc074ee82db6f98564830d","tid":455894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:27:54.000Z","msg":"樓主咪晒時間再諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你隻野行緊bridge mode <br />\n你部電腦攞緊public IP<br />\n隻router transparent緊 無ip入唔返㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7473f73f35993b5378f689ae19460dceafea9f41","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim