家onsite 捉住你手仔幫你搵掂佢"},{"pid":"8f8a4677d07d1f1b68f4128bb97106cd8c132071","tid":455894,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Google 下你隻野點reset 啦 <br />\n應該有d recovery tools</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連<a href=\"http://www.routerlogin.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.routerlogin.net&d=cPaJDcXG9XQolH6S26n0ssn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3fe739c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.routerlogin.net</a>都入唔到　reset 唔到</blockquote><br />\nHardware reset囉 部部機都有<br />\n唔一定要login 到 <br />\n磚左都救到<br />\nGoogle 啦屌 上官網睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有禁過好多次架啦其實<br />\n但無改變炸</blockquote><br />\n屌有procedure 㗎啦 官網咪有教囉 跟返型號搵<br />\n大個仔啦 咪撚成條女咁啦<br />\n一係你比五千蚊我 我依家onsite 捉住你手仔幫你搵掂佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試咗好多次吉完佢都係就咁重開"},{"pid":"632c5bff81249a4e7baacddc3947f73d766cb60f","tid":455894,"uid":75871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"吉幾耐呀<br />\n開住機吉實三秒 吉住重開 開完等多三秒"},{"pid":"b4bc55a97115cf59d03e03d179d55f5829dc1654","tid":455894,"uid":99582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Google 下你隻野點reset 啦 <br />\n應該有d recovery tools</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連<a href=\"http://www.routerlogin.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.routerlogin.net&d=cPaJDcXG9XQolH6S26n0ssn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3fe739c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.routerlogin.net</a>都入唔到　reset 唔到</blockquote><br />\nHardware reset囉 部部機都有<br />\n唔一定要login 到 <br />\n磚左都救到<br />\nGoogle 啦屌 上官網睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我有禁過好多次架啦其實<br />\n但無改變炸</blockquote><br />\n屌有procedure 㗎啦 官網咪有教囉 跟返型號搵<br />\n大個仔啦 咪撚成條女咁啦<br />\n一係你比五千蚊我 我依家onsite 捉住你手仔幫你搵掂佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試咗好多次吉完佢都係就咁重開</blockquote><br />\n你比六千我 我幫你含住搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52af811ccbed1a42808da2354e7dd23aadef7d13","tid":455894,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:06:11.000Z","msg":"Press the reset button, and if that doesn't work, do a 30/30/30 reset. Hold the reset button for 30 seconds, then unplug the router while still holding the reset button for 30 seconds, then plug the router back in while holding the reset button, so overall you have held it down for 1minute 30seconds. If this doesn't work, connect to your router with your terminal.<br />\n<br />\n樓主係咪唔撚識google"}]}